OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,FPep Guardiola has responded to Sir Jim
OL,8,FRatcliffe's comments about immigration
OL,9,Fby saying people need to "embrace
OL,10,Fother cultures" to make a "better
OL,11,Fsociety".
OL,13,FManchester United minority owner
OL,14,FRatcliffe this week sparked
OL,15,Fcontroversy by claiming the UK had
OL,16,Fbeen "colonised" by immigrants.
