OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,FRatcliffe has since apologised for any
OL,8,Foffence caused by his remarks, which
OL,9,FGuardiola acknowledged, but the
OL,10,FManchester City manager feels the
OL,11,Fwider issue of how countries treat
OL,12,Fimmigrants remains a "big problem".
OL,14,FGuardiola said at a press conference:
OL,15,F"I have a huge appreciation for Sir
OL,16,FJim. I was fortunate to meet him. He
OL,17,Fmade a statement after to apologise.
