OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,F"I'm not commenting on what Sir Jim
OL,8,FRatcliffe said because after that he
OL,9,Fsaid what exactly he wanted to say,
OL,10,Fbut all around the world the problem
OL,11,Fthat we have in all the countries (is
OL,12,Fthat) we treat immigrants or people
OL,13,Fwho come from other countries as the
OL,14,Fproblem for problems that our
OL,15,Fcountries have and it is a big, big,
OL,16,Fbig, big, big problem.
OL,18,F"The fact that I am a Catalan and you
OL,19,Fare British ` what influence did we
OL,20,Fhave on where we were born? It was mum
OL,21,Fand dad.
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@AOU
