OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,F"Everybody wants to have a better life
OL,8,Fand a perspective to have a better
OL,9,Ffuture for themselves, their families
OL,10,Fand their friends, and sometimes
OL,11,Fopportunities come in the place where
OL,12,Fyou are born and the place that maybe
OL,13,Fyou go.
OL,15,F"Before it was so difficult to travel,
OL,16,Fbut today in one hour you can be
OL,17,Feverywhere. Today the colour of the
OL,18,Fskin or where you were born doesn't
OL,19,Fmake a difference. We have a lot of
OL,20,Fwork to do about that.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
