OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,F"It doesn't make me feel that because
OL,8,FI am Catalan I am better than you. My
OL,9,Feducation when I was born and
OL,10,Ftravelled in Mexico and Qatar or lived
OL,11,Fin Italy or England or Germany, that
OL,12,Fis just the benefit of my personality.
OL,14,F"I met incredibly nice people
OL,15,Ftravelling and that is what it is
OL,16,Fabout, but it doesn't make me feel
OL,17,Fbetter just for the fact I was born in
OL,18,Fone place or the other one.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
