OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,F"Most people are running away from
OL,8,Fcountries because of problems in their
OL,9,Fcountries, not because they want to
OL,10,Fleave. As much as we embrace other
OL,11,Fcultures ` truly, truly embrace it `
OL,12,Fthat will be a better society."
OL,14,FRatcliffe's comments in a Sky News
OL,15,Finterview on Wednesday were heavily
OL,16,Fcriticised by Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,17,FStarmer and the Mayor of Greater
OL,18,FManchester Andy Burnham.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@_O]
