OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,FRatcliffe's claims will also be
OL,8,Fexamined by the Football Association
OL,9,Fto see whether they brought the game
OL,10,Finto disrepute, while on Thursday
OL,11,Fafternoon Manchester United issued a
OL,12,Fstatement saying the club take pride
OL,13,Fin being "inclusive and welcoming".
OL,15,FIt read: "Our diverse group of
OL,16,Fplayers, staff and global community of
OL,17,Fsupporters, reflect the history and
OL,18,Fheritage of Manchester; a city that
OL,19,Fanyone can call home.
