OL,3,CCity manager Pep Guardiola responds to
OL,4,CSir Jim Ratcliffe after immigrant
OL,5,Ccomment
OL,7,F"Since launching All Red All Equal in
OL,8,F2016, we have embedded equality,
OL,9,Fdiversity and inclusion into
OL,10,Feverything we do.
OL,12,F"We remain deeply committed to the
OL,13,Fprinciples and spirit of that
OL,14,Fcampaign."
